      "topics": [],
      "summary": "",
      "learning_objectives": [
        "Define content coupling and describe how one module directly uses or modifies another module's code.",
        "Identify examples of content coupling, such as jumping into another module\u2019s code.",
        "Explain why content coupling is considered the highest and most undesirable degree of coupling.",
        "Recognize that modern high\u2011level languages (e.g., C) do not support content coupling."
      ],
